2018/12/10 12:14PM (AEST)

It is now possible to specify per-conference semaphores for echomail. Under
the main section of the conference add the option:

semaphore = /path/to/new.semaphore

If this doesn't exist, it will use the echomail semaphore in bbs.ini.

2018/12/10 8:00AM (AEST)

You will need to run "users_sql_update.pl" on your users database.

Added string 295, see STRINGS.CHANGES for details.
